-- U.S. Bancorp to buy Montana's United Financial
-- 
-- Mon Nov 6, 2006 5:56pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2006/11/06/us-financial-unitedfinancial-usbancorp-idUSWEN923720061106

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - U.S. Bancorp. ( USB.N ), the sixth-largest U.S. bank, said on Monday that it had agreed to buy Montana's United Financial Corp. UBMT.O for about $22.91 a share in stock based on current stock prices. 

 U.S. Bancorp is offering 0.6825 of its shares for each share of United Financial, the parent company of Heritage Bank, in the stock-for-stock deal, the companies said in a statement.